title: QA Engineer Interview
Interview Descriptions: The interview process typically includes the following steps One technical round discussion around 45 min followed by Managerial round discussion then HR round discussions.. Total process will take then week
Interview Questions: Basic CURD Operations in API automation

title: Office Manager Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 weeks. I interviewed at Kairos (Medford, OR)
Interview Descriptions: 3 person panel who took turns asking questions really excellent questions. Comfortable and supportive environment with easy going, kind people. When I didn’t  quite understand one of the questions, the gentleman gave helpful examples and Never rushed me.
Interview Questions: How do you handle or react to the stress that occurs when many things are happening at once.

title: Programmer Analyst Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 months. I interviewed at Kairos in Feb 2018
Interview Descriptions: Good job during the interview and hiring process. A lot of information around position requirements and expectations which helped make an informed decision. I am very satisfied with their communication throughout the process.
